{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"be559f93ef","title":"文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"55c57b8178","index":0,"year":1966,"month":4,"day":22,"articleId":"be559f93ef"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e01144d6a6","type":"title","text":"文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"be559f93ef"},{"id":"61bb01340f","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"be559f93ef"},{"id":"8fdd795931","type":"paragraph","text":"我不相信，在文化革命中的问题只是吴晗问题，后面还有一串串“三家村”。文化革命是触及人们灵魂的革命，是意识形态的斗争，触及的很广泛，涉及面很宽。朝里有人，比如中央宣传部、中央文化部都发生这方面的问题，朝里都有人。各大区、各省市都有。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"be559f93ef"},{"id":"ec65b6e422","type":"paragraph","text":"在党中央各部门，包括大区、各省市，朝里是否那么干净？我不相信。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"be559f93ef"}],"page":{"id":"24675a7dc8","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"be559f93ef","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}